hotspot.description: Welcome to Nazareth Catholic College! At our College, a partnership of learning exists between our students, the College and your family. Our program focus is successful learning for all, challenging deep thinking, and recognising and reflecting your child's aspirations, interests and skill-sets.
hotspot.title: Welcome!

hotspot.description: Our Music programs at Nazareth Catholic College aim to provide music education of the highest quality. With a balance of traditional musical concepts and innovative musical experience, we instill in our students the relevance of music education in our society.
hotspot.title: Music Program
